Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.79,0:00:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago there existed a brilliant young scientist.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.79,0:00:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,By dint of his astonishing genius,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.76,0:00:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,he was able to make a number of \Ncontributions to human knowledge.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.03,0:00:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, however, he became \Ndisillusioned with the world.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:30.70,0:00:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Though constantly showered with praise for the subtlety of his mind,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:33.48,0:00:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,none of his ideas or theories ever received
Dialogue: 10,0:00:36.86,0:00:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,even the slightest support from the scientific community.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.89,0:00:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,"We should not be striving to advance human civilization,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.63,0:00:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather the artificial evolution of humans as a species."
Dialogue: 10,0:00:51.68,0:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the only dream he had ever had,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.62,0:00:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but not a single person came forward to help him fulfill that dream.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn these apes!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.78,0:01:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dangerous ideas"? Writing about me as if I were some freak...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.19,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do they really think humans have come this far by avoiding risks?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.30,0:01:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiots who think they no longer need to evolve
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.05,0:01:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,have no right to pass on their genes!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.14,0:01:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, this plan was always for my own sake.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.08,0:01:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I will carry it out... Even if I must do it all myself!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.85,0:01:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thereafter, he devoted himself to research.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.94,0:01:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only after he turned 70 that his efforts began to yield results.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.19,0:01:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,First, the scientist regained his youth.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:48.98,0:01:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, he began cloning himself.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.67,0:01:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He named his laboratory the "House of Evolution",
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.68,0:01:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and together with his clones
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.38,0:02:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,he conducted countless experiments with animals to create new species.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.58,0:02:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Eventually, his experiments shifted to human subjects—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.57,0:02:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,This is taking too long!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.02,0:02:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.16,0:02:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this got to do with me? \NYou're just trying to act cool again.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.61,0:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get to the point, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.78,0:02:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei is a busy man. \NSummarize it in 20 words or less.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:24.99,0:02:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.05,0:04:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in other words, my boss has become very curious about your body.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.30,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not interested in dudes.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.81,0:04:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you misunderstood, Sensei.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.85,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He plans to use your body, \Nwhich surpasses normal human limitations,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.90,0:04:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,for his research on evolution.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.28,0:04:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do something, I'm sure he'll try again.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot allow him a free hand.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Our move should be to attack him.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, let's go.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.08,0:04:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.25,0:04:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.00,0:04:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Now?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.25,0:04:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, there's a sale on tomorrow. Can't do it then.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.92,0:04:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This doesn't sound good. Better tell the Doctor...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.97,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.93,0:04:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.26,0:04:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have one last question.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.06,0:04:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the "House of Evolution" developing cyborgs prior to four years ago?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.27,0:04:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How many more cyborgs are there?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.90,0:05:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any of them destroyed towns in the past?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.53,0:05:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.65,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,but at the "House of Evolution", I'm the only combat cyborg.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.66,0:05:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.20,0:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Our elite force, formed for the extermination of these obsolete humans, was wiped out?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.71,0:05:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,According to Armored Gorilla's report, \Nthe two responsible are on their way here.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.38,0:05:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,If they come,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.55,0:05:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,all our research, everything we've \Nbeen working on, could be destroyed.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a serious matter.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.02,0:05:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The only option is to use our trump card.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.94,0:05:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin preparations for the release of Carnage Kabuto.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.19,0:05:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.86,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not him!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.57,0:05:45.69,Default - Up,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll finally be released?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.12,0:05:49.20,Default - Up,,0,0,0,,He's right. That might be the only way.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But maybe we should stop him.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.86,Default - Up,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.27,0:05:53.41,Default - Up,,0,0,0,,Is that the only way?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.41,0:05:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Be calm! He will be our last resort.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.54,0:05:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.21,0:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,For now we'll activate all of \Nour traps from floors 01 to 08.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.59,0:06:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're lucky, they will take care of the intruders.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fully aware of what will happen to me
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.30,0:06:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,should we fail.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.81,0:06:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think we'd be running the whole way.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How else are we gonna get there?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.56,0:06:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure you could fly or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.11,0:06:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans can't fly, you know.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that you are never late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You are a true hero.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.03,0:06:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I hardly ever arrive on time.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:35.66,0:06:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place that Gorilla told us about.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.88,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...the "House of Evolution".
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.13,0:06:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, three, four, five, six...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it's about eight stories high—
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.06,0:07:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... what was that all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.19,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I decided it would be most efficient to destroy them all in one fell swoop.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.66,0:07:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We could have at least seen what the bad guys had in store for us.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.91,0:07:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That was kind of mean.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.13,0:07:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there's a basement.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.56,0:07:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.24,0:08:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Carnage Kabuto.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you well?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It appears you've killed a bunch of my clones again.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.34,0:08:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Satisfied?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.84,0:08:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Why would I be satisfied?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.89,0:08:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been kept locked up deep beneath the Earth.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.72,0:08:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Me! The strongest warrior in the entire "House of Evolution".
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.73,0:08:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You are mentally unstable.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.73,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We couldn't control you. There was no choice.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.49,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Control? You moron!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.95,0:08:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the culmination of the "New Human" you guys have sought for so long.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.62,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My intelligence and physical strength are incomparable to your own!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.75,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You{\i0} should be the ones obeying {\i1}me{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.42,0:08:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No. You're a failure.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.97,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's true you perform at unheard of levels,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it is humanity you lack.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.39,0:09:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead, kill me. Plenty of clones could take my place.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.35,0:09:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a favor to ask first.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.73,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a specimen I must have.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.99,0:09:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He is extremely strong. Only you can defeat him.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.37,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want you to catch him for me...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...dead or alive.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.15,0:09:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This basement is huge!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting kind of fired up.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.82,0:09:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I sense living beings further ahead...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:40.18,0:09:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, two of them are approaching.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, here we go!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.82,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two. Which one is it?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.52,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The one on the right...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:52.94,0:09:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, you don't need the one on the left!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.47,0:09:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Genos?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.12,0:10:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.83,0:10:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Carnage Kabuto!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.60,0:10:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We got a combat experimentation room.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.21,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.47,0:10:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You turned Genos into a piece of modern art.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.97,0:10:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight's on!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.23,0:10:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty big, eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.07,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the biggest room in the facility.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.98,0:10:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is where they make us fight \Nto test our combat abilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.54,0:10:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's start the killing—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.41,0:10:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.73,0:10:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Still alive, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.82,0:11:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Machinegun Blows!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.87,0:11:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He got me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,... take him...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.84,0:11:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Your face is all cracked. Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,With his breath? Impossible!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.69,0:11:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Genos, you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.44,0:11:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.94,0:12:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're not! Look at your head!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.04,0:12:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gone and gotten my hopes up.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.98,0:12:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have always been critical of \Nhumans and their inferior abilities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.07,0:12:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The entire species, aside from myself, \Nshould be viewed only as dumb animals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.22,0:12:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That realization was agony for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.26,0:12:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If memory serves, I was 15 when it occurred to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:52.35,0:12:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A plan to evolve the human animal{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.04,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and create a world where I could live contentedly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.92,0:13:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A utopia of my own, created by me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.84,0:13:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A world made up of only us,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.26,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the new human breed that will transcend humanity!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I must see it through.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.07,0:13:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compared to my anguish back then, \Nthis physical pain I feel now is nothing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.66,0:13:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the hold up? Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me all you've got.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.87,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Carnage Kabuto—a demon incarnate,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the strongest and most brutal \Ncreation of the House of Evolution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.63,0:13:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's see how you, at your archaic \Nstage of human development,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:42.96,0:13:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}fare against a monster that is the final form of artificial evolution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.76,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or will you be the trigger for a new evolution?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't wait to find out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.31,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see it. I see it! You're supposed to be strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.52,0:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't disappoint me now.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.66,0:14:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You're this place's ultimate weapon, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.36,0:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're clearly not the same as \Nthe guys from this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.41,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at you, just oozing with confidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.25,0:14:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Such speed!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.89,0:14:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He just backed off?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.48,0:14:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Carnage Kabuto?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:40.69,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I'd attacked him just now, he'd have killed me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.44,0:14:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who the hell is this guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.29,0:14:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's leaving himself wide open,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.40,0:14:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet all my instincts are screaming, sending out danger signals!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.99,0:14:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.42,0:15:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell did you get that strong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you wanna know too?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.77,0:15:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Genos, you listen carefully too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.89,0:15:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's going to tell us right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The secret to Sensei's power...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.73,0:15:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know too.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.86,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.99,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Genus.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:36.16,0:15:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, fine. Listen up.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.91,0:15:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's too risky! He can't let these guys know his secret!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.83,0:15:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First, what's important is, to make sure \Nyou stick to this intense training regimen.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.80,0:15:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Training? Not modification surgery or genetic enhancement,{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.35,0:15:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but training?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.10,0:16:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What training...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Genos.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.44,0:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You just have to keep doing it.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how hard it gets.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.70,0:16:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It took me three years to get this strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.28,0:16:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred push-ups! One hundred sit-ups!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One hundred squats!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.50,0:16:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a ten kilometer run.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.05,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single day!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.76,0:16:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course, make sure you eat three meals a day.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.47,0:16:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a banana in the morning is fine. But the most important thing is
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.69,0:16:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to never use the A/C or heat in the summer or winter.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,In the beginning, you'll wish you were dead.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.16,0:16:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You might start thinking, \N"where's the harm in taking a day off?"
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.24,0:17:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But for me, in order to be a strong hero, no matter how tough it was,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.60,0:17:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I was spitting blood, I never stopped.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.42,0:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept doing squats even when my legs were so heavy they refused to move.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.34,0:17:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when my arms started making weird clicking noises,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept doing push-ups.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.94,0:17:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A year and a half later, I started to notice a difference.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:24.10,0:17:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I was bald...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I had become stronger!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:30.07,0:17:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, you gotta train like hell to the point where your hair falls out.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.86,0:17:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the only way to become strong.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys that are fooling around with
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.62,0:17:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,the "new human race" and evolution junk will never make it this far.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.21,0:17:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Human beings are strong because we have the ability to change ourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}W-What?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.84,0:17:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is this guy... for real?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.63,0:17:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.18,0:18:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You are so...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.17,0:18:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,full of crap!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:03.85,0:18:05.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.02,0:18:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That is nothing but standard strength training!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.07,0:18:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's not even that intense! It's just a normal level!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.27,0:18:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I have to get stronger. I didn't ask to study under you just to hear jokes!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:23.62,0:18:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Saitama-sensei,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.04,0:18:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,your power is clearly stronger than what you'd get from just training your body.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right, I want to know your—{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to know your true secret!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.05,0:18:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Genos...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You may not believe me, but that's really all I did.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.85,0:18:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Carnage Kabuto!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.65,0:18:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't wanna tell us your secret... so be it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:57.69,0:19:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! You'll go on another rampage!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:01.07,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you aren't stronger than me anyway!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.54,0:19:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But, since you pissed me off,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.46,0:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna annihilate you.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:18.17,0:19:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Carnage Mode!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.43,0:19:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,When I get like this I lose control for a whole week
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.73,0:19:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and my lust for death cannot be quelled!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.53,0:19:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,After I kill you, I'll head into town and go on a killing rampage until next Saturday!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.86,0:19:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are indeed a strong hero, then try and stop me!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.86,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way... it can't be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.98,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.11,0:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dammit. I may have made a horrible mistake.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.69,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This guy's in Carnage Mode...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.63,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He said he'll be on a rampage for a whole week?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.79,0:20:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Death, death, death, death, death, death!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.29,0:20:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Death, death, death, death, death!!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.87,0:20:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He'll be like this till next Saturday?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.86,0:20:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One whole week from today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next Saturday...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.13,0:20:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In other words, today is Saturday too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.75,0:20:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That means...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.36,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all over.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.56,0:20:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no one in this world that can stop him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.59,0:21:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That means... Today is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.34,0:21:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Bargain day at the supermarket!!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.99,0:21:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who the hell is this guy?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.09,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I screwed up!!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is he—{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.17,0:21:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure he's upset about this.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:30.68,0:21:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei, the store closes at 10pm.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.02,0:21:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That is about four hours away. \NIf we really hurry, we can make it.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.48,0:21:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make it if I hurry?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:41.73,0:21:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.44,0:21:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Genos!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.69,0:21:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Sensei!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.78,0:21:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I think I'm done with evolution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.66,0:21:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It appears... I am the one who must change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:23:32.55,0:23:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. The on-site investigation is underway.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:36.68,0:23:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's correct.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:39.27,0:23:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like the other cases, the area has \Nbeen thoroughly burnt by intense flames.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:43.63,0:23:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything points to the young \Ncyborg being responsible for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:48.82,0:23:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, understood.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:52.69,0:23:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Such a devastating amount of power.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:57.46,0:23:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:00.75,0:24:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, this is Carnage Kabuto. In Japanese my name is "Ashura Kabuto",
Dialogue: 10,0:24:04.38,0:24:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and the kanji comes from "Shell", "Field Trip", and the Sanskrit word "Aum".
Dialogue: 10,0:24:09.46,0:24:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddaya think? You don't give a damn, eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:24:12.09,0:24:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: One Punch Man episode 4, "The Modern Ninja".
Dialogue: 10,0:24:16.77,0:24:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So that guy is finally gonna show up?